title: Bobby Got Rid of Beloved Personal Item and It Pained Him + Eddie Updates Us On His Bologna Sandwich Lesson + Amy Got Her Daughter Her First iPhone Was Shocked By Her Lock Screen
itunes:title: Bobby Got Rid of Beloved Personal Item and It Pained Him + Eddie Updates Us On His Bologna Sandwich Lesson + Amy Got Her Daughter Her First iPhone Was Shocked By Her Lock Screen
description:
Bobby shares that he has been decluttering his home and had to get rid of something that he had to get rid of after 15 years. Eddie gives us an update on his bologna sandwich lesson (or punishment depending on how you look at it...) he gave his son…was he able to get his grades up? Amy bought her daughter her first iPhone and thought it was interesting the wallpaper she picked.
